00:56:40.918 --> 00:56:44.713 line:90% position:50% align:center
This month’s postcard comes from Liberia.

00:56:44.713 --> 00:56:47.716 line:90% position:50% align:center
Nestled on the coast of western Africa,

00:56:47.716 --> 00:56:51.470 line:90% position:50% align:center
Liberia’s terrain
includes stunning landscapes,

00:56:51.470 --> 00:56:56.225 line:90% position:50% align:center
sandy beaches,
rolling hills, and lush rainforests.

00:56:58.435 --> 00:57:00.437 line:90% position:50% align:center
English is the official language,

00:57:00.437 --> 00:57:04.233 line:90% position:50% align:center
spoken alongside
over 20 indigenous languages.

00:57:04.233 --> 00:57:07.403 line:90% position:50% align:center
Liberia, which means “The Land of the Free,”

00:57:07.403 --> 00:57:11.073 line:90% position:50% align:center
was established in 1821 as a safe haven

00:57:11.073 --> 00:57:14.493 line:90% position:50% align:center
for freed slaves from the United States.

00:57:14.493 --> 00:57:17.913 line:90% position:50% align:center
Over 60 years later,
the truth began to spread,

00:57:17.913 --> 00:57:20.499 line:90% position:50% align:center
and with the help from missionaries,

00:57:20.499 --> 00:57:24.044 line:90% position:50% align:center
the first congregation was formed in 1948.

00:57:24.795 --> 00:57:27.756 line:90% position:50% align:center
From 1989 to 2003,

00:57:27.756 --> 00:57:32.594 line:90% position:50% align:center
Liberia endured devastating civil wars
that affected thousands,

00:57:32.594 --> 00:57:35.097 line:90% position:50% align:center
including our brothers and sisters.

00:57:36.348 --> 00:57:39.935 line:90% position:50% align:center
Despite the hardship,
they stayed positive.

00:57:39.935 --> 00:57:44.732 line:90% position:50% align:center
One brother who had to flee
his home three times said:

00:57:44.732 --> 00:57:47.609 line:90% position:50% align:center
“These are the conditions we preach about;

00:57:47.609 --> 00:57:50.779 line:90% position:50% align:center
we are living in the last days.”

00:57:50.779 --> 00:57:53.782 line:90% position:50% align:center
Today, Jehovah’s Witnesses in Liberia

00:57:53.782 --> 00:57:56.452 line:90% position:50% align:center
continue to see excellent results.

00:57:56.452 --> 00:57:59.330 line:90% position:50% align:center
For example, the East Ganta Congregation,

00:57:59.330 --> 00:58:01.999 line:90% position:50% align:center
with only 103 publishers,

00:58:01.999 --> 00:58:04.209 line:90% position:50% align:center
had an impressive Memorial attendance

00:58:04.209 --> 00:58:08.714 line:90% position:50% align:center
of 964 in 2024.

00:58:09.298 --> 00:58:12.509 line:90% position:50% align:center
The brothers
had to meet in five different locations

00:58:12.509 --> 00:58:14.428 line:90% position:50% align:center
to accommodate everyone.

00:58:14.428 --> 00:58:16.096 line:90% position:50% align:center
In Robertsport,

00:58:16.096 --> 00:58:18.932 line:90% position:50% align:center
local families highly respect the Bible

00:58:18.932 --> 00:58:22.102 line:90% position:50% align:center
and often gather to hear the good news.

00:58:22.102 --> 00:58:26.023 line:90% position:50% align:center
The Robertsport Congregation
sends their love and greetings

00:58:26.023 --> 00:58:28.442 line:90% position:50% align:center
to the worldwide brotherhood.

00:58:29.443 --> 00:58:32.946 line:90% position:50% align:center
From the World Headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:58:32.946 --> 00:58:36.367 line:90% position:50% align:center
this is JW Broadcasting.

